description: EU leaders are set to meet on 18 July to discuss a Covid-19 recovery fund.
title: Denmark's PM cancels wedding to attend EU summit
title_page: Denmark's PM cancels wedding to attend EU summit - BBC News
maintext: Writing on Facebook, Ms Frederiksen said: "I am so looking forward to marrying this amazing man. But obviously it shouldn't be easy, and now the Council meeting in Brussels has been convened precisely on Saturday in July, when we had planned a wedding."
